{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Medusa is sat relaxing in the Temple of Ares when soldiers storm in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Athena, having decided Medusa's curse wasn't severe enough, sent her followers to get her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Medusa must use her curse and her wits to her advantage to evade capture and punish the bratty goddess that betrayed her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn based stealth puzzle gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay hidden from sight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn enemies to stone when it suits you, don't let them block your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use them to block vision from other enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't let them get you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cute and stylised art style, with beautiful minimalist tilesets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A bunch of puzzles, ranging from simple to mind bending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Casual difficulty, even the hardest puzzles can be beaten with trial and error.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487590/extras/medusa_portrait_1.png?t=1739078832\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739078832","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487590/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739078832","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487590/fc82a866b4d7ed5a0dd5550cc3e2dbce47dd5c5d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739078832","ca